node.text: I am so proud of my friend Sparkle she told me she had a Dream, and she went to school got certified and started her event planning company called @pinkblissevents .I remember when she started and now she is planning some of the most beautiful events I have seen. I am looking forward to her doing my tea party. #sheready #MadHaddishteaparty #pinkblissevents

node.text:
My GOD THANK YOU!!!! FOR ALWAYS PUTTING ME IN A PLACE! WHERE I MAYBE SAFE, BUT YOU KEPT ME SAFE!!! IThank you 
Tiffany Haddish #sharkweek #sheready

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tiffany Haddish on July 07, 2021 tagging @kevinhart4real, and @tiffanyhaddish. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text:
Happy Birthday to my Little Big Brother. I am so Glad God put you on this earth. @kevinhart4real you have been a Great Brother, Teacher and BucketHead. I Am Grateful that you always pushing me when I needed it, and Ground me when I needed it, and making me Laugh when I need one. I wish you a hundred more Birthdays. Oh and I know this is a Day late but this way I figured you would actually see it. From your Best Big little Sister I Love You.
Tiffany Haddish😘
